data.description: Escape to serenity just outside the city limits! This charming home sits on 2.88 acres of partially cleared land. Inside is new LVP floors throughout common areas and fresh paint throughout. The open concept kitchen boasts granite countertops and a freshly added coffee bar, perfect for entertaining. Tall ceilings enhance the spaciousness of the common areas. The primary bedroom features a tray ceiling and a spacious bathroom with a custom walk-in shower, jetted tub, and room for a second vanity. Step outside to the back patio and enjoy a serene lookout surrounded by fruit trees, leading to a flat backyard—ideal for outdoor gatherings or a peaceful escape. Located in the sought-after Sheridan School District, this home offers a perfect blend of tranquility and modern living.
